Little Neck Parkway, west side, opposite East Williston Ave. (formerly Lawrence Ave.), showing the G. Rhodes house in 1873; B. Rhodes in 1891; and J. Wick from 1896-1934.
1922.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
